description: In this volume collecting stories from SUPERGIRL #10-19 and the INFINITE HOLIDAY SPECIAL #1, Supergirl finally adopts a secret identity, joins the super-team the Outsiders, battles Batgirl, and begins a relationship with her new boyfriend, Power Boy!

description: The rest of his fellow cops are dealing with a blackout. His partner is dealing with problems of her own. The only one who can take down the villain who started all this trouble? New York's own John McClane! It's his first case as a detective. Could it be his last?
name: Die Hard: Year One #8

description: Dracula is a name that stands for epitome of evil and instills terror among his victims. He is a legend in the land of Romania which is rife with the stories of his exploits! Dracula is no ordinary vampire who could he warded off by cross or sunlight! He could be killed only by the bones of a saint. Saint Ulogion sacrificed his life, so that his bones could become the ultimate weapon to kill Dracula. A cross was pierced in Dracula's coffin to thwart Dracula from coming alive! He was then buried in his own palace. He shall arise only when the cross is dislodged from his grave! Nagpasha and his mentor now wish to unleash the terror of Dracula and use him to kill Nagraj. They tried their best, but they were dismayed to discover that the cross could be dislodged only by a descendent of Saint Ulogion. But it seemed that it was their lucky day. Lori was visiting Dracula's palace and confided in her fiance that she was the last living descendant of Saint Ulogion. Will Lori be forced to dislodge the cross? What shall happen when Count Dracula arises from his grave? Will Dhruv and Lori manage to stop the most dangerous and almost immortal vampire that ever lived! Read a blood chilling adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Dracula ka Hamla
